	u32 to Ipv4Addr to match area ID type changes.

	* zebra-rs/src/ospf/config.rs: Update OspfNetworkConfig area_id
	type to Ipv4Addr. Add conversion from u32 input to Ipv4Addr in
	config parsing. Implement manual Default trait for
	OspfNetworkConfig.

