	variants to use Ipv4Addr for area_id parameter. Fix link_top()
	method to properly handle Option chaining with and_then().

	* zebra-rs/src/ospf/lsdb.rs (lookup_by_id): Implement proper LSA
	lookup using composite key (ls_id, adv_router). Fix return type to
	Option<&OspfLsa> to avoid unnecessary cloning.

	* zebra-rs/src/ospf/config.rs: Fix incorrect to_host_prefix() call
	on Ipv4Net. Remove unnecessary conversion as addr.prefix is already
	an Ipv4Net type.

	* zebra-rs/src/rib/router_id.rs: Fix IPv4 address extraction from
	LinkAddr. Use filter_map with pattern matching to properly extract
	Ipv4Addr from IpNet enum, handling only IPv4 variants.

	* zebra-rs/src/config/parse.rs: Implement comprehensive YANG choice
	statement parsing support. Add choice_states tracking to State
	struct. Implement is_choice_case() detection, automatic case
	switching, and directory filtering for inactive choice cases.

